Package com.salesforce.multicloudj.blob.gcp

Class GcpBlobClient

java.lang.Object
com.salesforce.multicloudj.blob.driver.AbstractBlobClient<GcpBlobClient>
com.salesforce.multicloudj.blob.gcp.GcpBlobClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
Provider, SdkService, AutoCloseable
@AutoService(AbstractBlobClient.class) public class GcpBlobClient extends AbstractBlobClient<GcpBlobClient>
An implementation of the AbstractBlobClient for GCP Cloud Storage. GcpBlobClient is service client for interacting with GCP Cloud Blob Storage.

This class provides methods to interact with GCP resources using GCP SDK for Java to interact with the Cloud Storage service.
